<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Mantles_with_pavilions">Mantles with pavilions</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Mantle_and_pavilion_(heraldry)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Mantles with pavilions"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
