			<div class="thumb" style="width: 150px; height: 150px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Koninklijk_Wapen_van_het_Koninkrijk_der_Nederlanden_(1907).jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="Coat of arms of the Dutch monarch, with a mantle and pavilion"><img alt="Coat of arms of the Dutch monarch, with a mantle and pavilion" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/23/Koninklijk_Wapen_van_het_Koninkrijk_der_Nederlanden_%281907%29.jpg/109px-Koninklijk_Wapen_van_het_Koninkrijk_der_Nederlanden_%281907%29.jpg" decoding="async" width="109" height="120" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/23/Koninklijk_Wapen_van_het_Koninkrijk_der_Nederlanden_%281907%29.jpg/164px-Koninklijk_Wapen_van_het_Koninkrijk_der_Nederlanden_%281907%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/23/Koninklijk_Wapen_van_het_Koninkrijk_der_Nederlanden_%281907%29.jpg/219px-Koninklijk_Wapen_van_het_Koninkrijk_der_Nederlanden_%281907%29.jpg 2x" data-file-width="995" data-file-height="1092" /></a></span></div>
			<div class="gallerytext"><a href="/wiki/Coat_of_arms_of_the_Netherlands" title="Coat of arms of the Netherlands">Coat of arms of the Dutch monarch</a>, with a mantle and pavilion</div>
		</li>
		<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px">
			<div class="thumb" style="width: 150px; height: 150px;"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:FranceRoyale.jpg" class="mw-file-description" title="Grand coat of arms of the Kingdom of France"><img alt="Grand coat of arms of the Kingdom of France" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6b/FranceRoyale.jpg/83px-FranceRoyale.jpg" decoding="async" width="83" height="120" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6b/FranceRoyale.jpg/124px-FranceRoyale.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6b/FranceRoyale.jpg/166px-FranceRoyale.jpg 2x" data-file-width="580" data-file-height="840" /></a></span></div>
